  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Oh, look who it is! The one who helped me out before. I had some pretty good mushroom stew thanks to you. Much appreciated. But now, the fairies in this village are telling me that the stew tastes a whole lot better if you throw in some #t2010005#."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "So, how about it? Could you gather some #b#t4000013#s#k for me one more time? And if you could pick up a #b#t2010005##k from the general store while you're at it, that'd be great. As you can see, I can't move a single inch from here because I have to guard the entrance to the forest I inherited from my father."
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "You're back! The #t4000013#s you brought this time looks even tastier than the last batch. Perfect! Now, if I just add this #t2010005#, I'll be able to whip up something truly amazing."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Thanks for the help. I think I'm going to have a very special dinner tonight, all thanks to you. As a reward, I'll give you another ore found in our forest. Take care of yourself out there!"
      },
